{"tid":1645911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"4女子在深水埗嘉頓山被人用刀襲擊受傷   一度昏迷　施襲男子在逃","createTime":"2019-10-11T05:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:56:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9c85b372c62de1374500819dc0babd6e77e836","tid":1645911,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485533-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485533-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=c4d387f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485533-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a5f06318\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485533-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-10-11 HKT 12:40<br />\n<br />\n深水埗嘉頓山發生傷人案，4名女子被人用刀襲擊受傷，有人一度昏迷，後來轉為清醒，施襲男子仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n案發在早上約10時，途人報案指一名男子持刀襲擊3名女子，男子逃走期間再襲擊多一名女子，有人胸和背部受刀傷，分別送往瑪嘉烈醫院和伊利沙伯醫院治理，4名傷者都沒有財物損失。<br />\n<br />\n警方正追緝一名男子，中等身材、約1.6米高，身穿T裇和長褲。"},{"pid":"f2464bf39eae50d68dea080115fc0f6221a03af3","tid":1645911,"uid":201112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"咩人？"},{"pid":"53a8fd74826a4fe8635f08c2da363e7ef454390e","tid":1645911,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f966d0319bf9f7417abce7cd84c09742cb200f","tid":1645911,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16e4894bac3a4d1957dda38b8e34e6c4a5ea993","